movies.title: Iron Jawed Angels
movies.plot: Defiant young activists take the women's suffrage movement by storm, putting their lives at risk to help American women win the right to vote.
movies.awards: Won 1 Golden Globe. Another 3 wins & 27 nominations.

movies.title: Mandela
movies.plot: Nelson Mandela becomes South Africa's first Black President, and was awarded the Nobel Peace Prize for his leadership in negotiating a bloodless revolution in that country.
movies.awards: Nominated for 1 Primetime Emmy. Another 6 wins & 4 nominations.

movies.title: Something the Lord Made
movies.plot: A dramatization of the relationship between heart surgery pioneers Alfred Blalock and Vivien Thomas.
movies.awards: Nominated for 2 Golden Globes. Another 17 wins & 30 nominations.
